<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Ldap - 标签 - w23ta0's blog</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/tags/ldap/</link><description>This is my new Hugo FixIt site</description><generator>Hugo 0.145.0 &amp; FixIt v0.3.16</generator><language>zh-cn</language><managingEditor>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</managingEditor><webMaster>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 11:36:22 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://w23ta0.github.io/tags/ldap/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>解决LDAP出现ldap_bind: Invalid credentials (49)错误</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20170314-%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3ldap%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0ldap-bind-invalid-credentials-49-%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF/</link><pubDate>Tue, 14 Mar 2017 14:43:23 +0000</pubDate><author>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</author><guid>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20170314-%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3ldap%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0ldap-bind-invalid-credentials-49-%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF/</guid><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%81/">身份认证</category><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/ldap/">LDAP</category><description>&lt;p>LDAP最经常遇到的就是ldap_bind: Invalid credentials (49)错误，本文阐述了错误原因及解决办法：
比如在某LDAP客户端，使用rootdn(管理员)权限为某用户修改密码时&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">$ ldappasswd -H ldap://172.16.0.21 -x -D &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;cn=admin,ou=People,dc=expmale,dc=com&amp;#34;&lt;/span> -W -S &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;uid=zhang3,ou=People,dc=expmale,dc=com&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">New password: 
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Re-enter new password: 
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Enter LDAP Password: 
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">ldap_bind: Invalid credentials &lt;span class="o">(&lt;/span>49&lt;span class="o">)&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;strong>错误原因1：管理员DN或者用户DN错误&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>管理员DN是在&lt;code>/etc/openldap/slapd.conf&lt;/code>中指定的rootdn，其格式
应该是”cn=admin,dc=expmale,dc=com”
而不是”cn=admin,ou=People,dc=expmale,dc=com”
而普通用户的DN才应该是”uid=zhang3,ou=People,dc=expmale,dc=com”。
也可以执行如下命令查看该用户的DN是否存在&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>CentOS6 安装配置OpenLDAP Server</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20170314-centos6-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEldap-server/</link><pubDate>Tue, 14 Mar 2017 12:13:46 +0000</pubDate><author>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</author><guid>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20170314-centos6-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEldap-server/</guid><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%81/">身份认证</category><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/ldap/">LDAP</category><description>&lt;h2 id="安装及配置" class="heading-element">&lt;span>安装及配置&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#%e5%ae%89%e8%a3%85%e5%8f%8a%e9%85%8d%e7%bd%ae" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>首先使用如下命令查看是否已经安装 openldap：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># rpm -qa | grep openldap &lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">openldap-2.4.40-16.el6.x86_64
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">openldap-servers-sql-2.4.40-16.el6.x86_64
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">openldap-clients-2.4.40-16.el6.x86_64
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">openldap-servers-2.4.40-16.el6.x86_64
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">openldap-devel-2.4.40-16.el6.x86_64&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>若已经安装过，可以忽略此步骤&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="导入epel源" class="heading-element">&lt;span>导入epel源&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#%e5%af%bc%e5%85%a5epel%e6%ba%90" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h3>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">wget http://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/6/x86_64/epel-release-6-8.noarch.rpm
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">rpm –ivh epel-release-6-8.noarch.rpm&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="安装openldap" class="heading-element">&lt;span>安装openldap&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#%e5%ae%89%e8%a3%85openldap" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h3>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">yum -y install openldap openldap-*&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="配置openldap包括准备db_config和slapdconf" class="heading-element">&lt;span>配置openldap，包括准备DB_CONFIG和slapd.conf&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#%e9%85%8d%e7%bd%aeopenldap%e5%8c%85%e6%8b%ac%e5%87%86%e5%a4%87db_config%e5%92%8cslapdconf" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h3>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">cd&lt;/span> /etc/openldap/
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">cp /usr/share/openldap-servers/slapd.conf.obsolete slapd.conf
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">cp /usr/share/openldap-servers/DB_CONFIG.example /var/lib/ldap/DB_CONFIG&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="设置-openldap的管理员密码" class="heading-element">&lt;span>设置 openldap的管理员密码&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#%e8%ae%be%e7%bd%ae-openldap%e7%9a%84%e7%ae%a1%e7%90%86%e5%91%98%e5%af%86%e7%a0%81" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>首先要生成经处理后的明文密码：&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>LDAP服务器的概念和原理简单介绍</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20170312-ldap%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E5%92%8C%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D/</link><pubDate>Sun, 12 Mar 2017 11:33:45 +0000</pubDate><author>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</author><guid>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20170312-ldap%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E5%92%8C%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D/</guid><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%81/">身份认证</category><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/ldap/">LDAP</category><description>&lt;h2 id="目录服务" class="heading-element">&lt;span>目录服务&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#%e7%9b%ae%e5%bd%95%e6%9c%8d%e5%8a%a1" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>目录是一个为查询、浏览和搜索而优化的专业分布式数据库，它呈树状结构组织数据，就好象Linux/Unix系统中的文件目录一样。目录数据库和关系数据库不同，它有优异的读性能，但写性能差，并且没有事务处理、回滚等复杂功能，不适于存储修改频繁的数据。所以目录天生是用来查询的，就好象它的名字一样。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>